，\r\n    對公眾散布而犯之。\r\n前項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/109%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c2701%2c20200929%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,109,上訴,2701,20200929,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"2701","JDATE":"20200929","JTITLE":"詐欺"}